实，但不了解具体原因。对此，西北大学研究生院李院长回应称无法透露，需向公安机关了解案件情况。西安市长安区郭杜派出所表示，案件具体细节不便透露。#周刊君调查#多次致电延安大学，尚未联系到相关负责人。目前，案件有待进一步调查。"},"attached_info":"ClYIvpvIjZTvlooDEAMaCDcyMzA0MzkyIMHB6YsGMNwBOKEeQBVyCTQ5NTEwNTE3MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA8gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg==","detail_text":"51 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6391f327259d209eeee77cbc41051271_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1635553443.848458","card_id":"Q_495006942","target":{"id":495006942,"title":"如何看待小米 MIX4 在双十一叠加 88VIP 再降 300，仅 3699 元起？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/495006942","type":"question","created":1635388104,"answer_count":154,"follower_count":314,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[890,25405,409116,725059,961372],"comment_count":49,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"累积降价达到了1300元，还会继续降吗？ 相关问题：如何看待小米 MIX 4 在双十一价格大幅跳水？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IvpvIjZTvlooDEAMaCDcyMjgyNDkzIMiV6IsGMDE4ugJAFnIJNDk1MDA2OTQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-169d5ac01beea515fde45e119d1299b6_720w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1635553443.8496156","card_id":"Q_494785308","target":{"id":494785308,"title":"腾讯视频回应买会员后还得看广告，称「不在会员免广告特权范围」，从法律角度看，腾讯的做法是否合理？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/494785308","type":"question","created":1635300767,"answer_count":263,"follower_count":910,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[215,648,1497,6479,105508],"comment_count":69,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，各大视频平台相继宣布停止 VIP 会员的超前点播服务，受到不少用户好评。但是仍有不少会员表示，交了会员费的自己，“免广告”的待遇名不副实，平台的各种形式的广告依然时不时跳出来，这些广告形式甚至多达 12 种，严重影响自己的体验感。 记者发现，一些视频平台在针